<recipe>
<title>
Pumpkin Pie Spice Recipe
</title>
<details>
AUTHOR: I Heart Eating
PREP TIME: 5 minutes
TOTAL TIME: 5 minutes
COURSE: Condiment
CUISINE: American
KEYWORD: pumpkin spice, spices
SERVINGS: 2
</details>
<ingredients>
LARGE BATCH
3 tablespoons ground cinnamon
1 tablespoon ground nutmeg
1 tablespoon ground ginger
1 teaspoon ground allspice
</ingredients>
<instructions>
Combine the spices, and store in an airtight container.
</instructions>
<cuisine>American</cuisine></recipe>